Body: Description: We stopped getting logs to our SIEM, QRadar, from EPP. SIEM integration is toggled to on and we haven't made any changes to it. Toggling it on and off did not make any improvements.
What We've Learned Updated: performed the steps I received on the escalated ticket and forwarded the results in a Word file to the engineering team
Next Steps Updated: waiting on R&D for the next steps
